NITFPROT (  NITF_DATA *   ) 
 

Remove information from the ParseInfo object. NOT DELETE, here is the deal... When an object is removed the ParseInfo object passes back a handle to it and simply forgets about it. That dynamic memory then becomes your responsibility.

Parameters:
